     C*-------------------------------*
     C*  ..BEFORE 10 DAYS WORKING DAY
     C*-------------------------------*
     C           KEY2      SETGTAGDPL121
     C                     Z-ADD11        U       20
     C                     Z-ADD0         HMD
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    HCD
     C                     Z-ADD0         CNT     20
      *
     C           1         DO   10        I       20
     C                     SETOF                     20
